data.description:
This charming 1,056sqft home is quite a find in the quiet town of Whitewright, Texas. Built in 2003, this home has been beautifully maintained and sits on a spacious 1.13 acre lot featuring a detached barn with half concreate slab foundation and 2 spacious storage sheds! With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home is perfect for families or anyone looking for some extra space!

Upon entering the home, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting living room that flows into the kitchen and dining area. The kitchen features modern appliances, and the master bedroom is spacious and comfortable, with an en-suite bathroom.
Outside, you'll find a large yard with plenty of room to play or entertain. Imagine spending summer afternoons barbecuing with friends and family or simply enjoying the peace and quiet of the countryside. This mobile home is sure to impress. Don't miss your chance to make it yours!
